    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    preprocessCore,
    stats,
    sva,
    impute
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    rmarkdown,
    knitr,
    RTCGA.miRNASeq
Config/testthat/edition: 3
